Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.73,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My bike is perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.37,0:00:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Keizou, what about Zenba?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here, Linda! {ゼヤー! - w/e that is}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! What's our course?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.30,0:01:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We takin' the usual route to Hakone's turnpike and back?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.46,0:01:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, you're riding\N in my sidecar. {脇}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in already!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.29,0:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... He can slide his bike like that to turn it around.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! \NIt's like he's skating!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is awesome...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Linda!\NYou're the greatest!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Keizou, blow them away! {ぶっちぎっちまえ！}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.71,0:02:05.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.92,0:02:10.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,I used to sneak out all the time to watch this back when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.11,0:02:14.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,But now I'm in the thick of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.59,0:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.79,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, let me \Nride sometime!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Write down your \Nfavorite position...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.87,0:02:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much foreplay and afterplay you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.69,0:03:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what did you come back for?! \NYou're going to lose the race!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Those biker punks...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Haruma.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, none of us \Nhave ever beaten Zenba.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda sucks, don't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.14,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you're on my bike, it's heavier than usual,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so hold on tight, you're in for a bumpy ride!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are \Nyou trying to say?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.38,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not what you think, Zenba!\NIt wasn't me who bumped into you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Noro!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Noro's the one driving!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, seriously!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.25,0:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, someone's gonna die! Please, be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Norosuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.07,0:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, what's with you?\NYou're not lookin' too good.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That tanker trying to block us?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.87,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo. Whenever I try to slip past 'em, he cuts me off.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look the other lane is open.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.58,0:06:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not open! A car is headed straight for us!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.93,0:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a bike, but it's actually a car with a broken headlight!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, you've let your guard down now that you're out of danger,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm taking that slipstream!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.11,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come! Here I come!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A toll gate?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My nerves are shot, \NI think I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you having fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I always get a bad feeling \Nright before I wipe out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A bad feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the funny thing is...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.53,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you feel like you're gonna run over an empty can in the next corner,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I get this kinda "oh shit" feeling,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.81,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but by the time I realize, it's usually too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't worth a damn if it kicks in just before a turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time me and Hinako did it,\N I had the same "oh shit" feeling.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But, hey, what happens \Nhappens, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.18,0:07:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That was Linda. \NAre they completely nuts?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.05,0:07:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I thought that was the bullet train for a second there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.11,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. How far ahead did Maki get anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, to tell \Nyou the truth...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.50,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a virgin! \NI was kinda hoping to live a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.21,0:08:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If we wipe out, I'll be right there with you. You won't be alone then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why so slow, Maki?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.78,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By my calculations, I should've stayed in the lead for another minute or two.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Zenba for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.10,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! Today's no good, Kurata! The crosswinds, they're—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.48,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you shittin' me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show those beach boy bastards what the Demons are made of!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.62,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's show 'em what we're made of!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.62,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's Cobra! Cobra ambushed \Nus from behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them overtake us!\NKill 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.47,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you could come all the way out here? Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You fucking shitsnakes!{imma leave this in, unless someone thinks it's too ESL lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.29,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought we'd be stuck behind shitty riders like you all day long?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.34,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all be six-feet under before the cops even show up!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You really wanna mess \Nwith us?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, dipshits!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.72,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, shitbags!\NLinda rules!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! \NWe let another one through!{imma ignore the snake wordplay on his name}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.81,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra? More like Slowbra!\NYou ain't got shit on us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.70,0:10:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We were having a good time chasing after the boss,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.12,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but you bastards are blocking the middle of the road.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?\NMaki, you motherfucker!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kill 'im!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's focus on Linda first!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki! Start with Maki!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.29,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Zenba, we're way out ahead! \NThey don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't you think it's time we slowed down a little?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.69,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, let's see what you're made of. I'm gonna open her up a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra's boss should \Nstill be up ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him! \NZenba, we've found him!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,About 50 meters ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's fast. \NHe's insanely fast, Zenba.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go even faster!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.03,0:12:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't breathe... Zenba. \NLet's take a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.13,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, the wind is makin' it hard to breathe...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what kinda idiot it would be.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If it ain't Linda's very \Nown Zenba Naito.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.93,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought something\N smelled like shit,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so I knew you were around here somewhere, Ibu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You never change, \Neh, Zenba?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.65,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you see it, Cobra and Linda have been at it for ages.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.78,0:12:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's about time we found out who's the fastest on the coast road.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's got \Nthe biggest balls.{liberal, but it works, fite me}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout we \Nfinally settle things?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're talkin'!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, you're weighing me down, so hop on that one instead!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The fuck are you doing?! \NGet off, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you fuckin' kidding me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't take orders from you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take him back!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on, Zenba!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.51,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear that, family-man punk biker boy?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own \Ndamn business!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You middle-aged high schooler!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.03,0:13:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Credit where it's due, we both drive an RS Z2, so at least you've got taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you lose on specs and guts.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.51,0:13:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove it so hard you're gonna choke on it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, the undisputed star of the Hakkotsu Highway...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,will be me, Ibu Koijirou, the third head of Cobra!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure to meet ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.00,0:14:02.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,Zenba... for an idiot, your blocking is perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.78,0:14:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You got eyes in the back of your skull or what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And in crosswinds like this?! You've gotta be some kind of monster freak!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One fuck up and you're goin' straight to hell.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't afford to lose this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.64,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.09,0:14:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's there a naked woman with a doll over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.32,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?! Don't take your eyes off the road!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.55,0:14:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, eyes on \Nthe road or we die!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.58,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, bossman! \NSnap out of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.25,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx95}Why would a naked woman with a doll be wandering around the bypass at midnight?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.86,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot! This race is as good as mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya! And maybe \Ndie while you're at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's that \Nlady with the doll?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Z-Zenba, eyes on the road!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.14,0:15:45.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm Haruma Yuuki. \NYou'd better remember it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.05,0:15:49.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,For starters, full marks in guts! Other school stuff, not so hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.24,0:15:54.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,And I'm a member of a gang I admire,\N Linda, Winds of Cemetery!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.83,0:16:01.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,And this is the apartment where the leader of Linda, Zenba, lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! \NZenba, hope you're well!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to escort \Nyou this morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yuuki? \NGood morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you recovered already? {from your injuries in that incident}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nothin' to worry about!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.74,0:16:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't force yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.94,0:16:41.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,That daddy is our leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, he burped.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My, good boy!{note - not watched so can't tell if Perevo mis-gendered the kid}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Yuuki, \NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.88,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, make sure he actually gets to work, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.37,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.00,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't trust him, but it's just in case.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.50,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it! I, Haruma, will see to it personally!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's all yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.54,0:17:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, but you know I did a real number on my bike the other night.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.45,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. I'll drive \Nyou around anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real stand-up guy, Haruma.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't your brother go to school with my Hinako?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.87,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but that was the only way I could join you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.83,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I'm part of Linda, I'm really stoked! I mean it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Zenba!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey there, kitty-cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You got any cash on you? \NWanna go grab a drink?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Leader, you need \Nto get to work!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.57,0:18:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I first saw Linda when I was back in middle school, and, well, I dunno, I just...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.58,0:18:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Zenba!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya! You got any cash on you? \NWanna go grab a drink?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.84,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided that I'd do whatever it took to get into Linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where we goin'?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.57,0:18:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, "Daddy!"\NWhat about work?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. \NIs that your son, Zenba?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.51,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm training under the leader to become a real man!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.25,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Training, eh? Come to think of it, I'm just one short.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The first 98 were easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.37,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I hooked up and settled down with Hinako,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.94,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for some reason, I just can't score that last one.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.63,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a fuckin' break! \NI'm only one off hitting 100!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Zenba, all the more reason for us to take care of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.67,0:19:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you got it!\NHaruma, lend me some money!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. \NYou're broke?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even \Npay the hotel fee?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, mister!\NWhat's even going through that head?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Wait a minute, \Nbaby! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.59,0:19:41.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,He's only a year older than me, \Nhe's got a babe for a wife and a kid...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,but he's like an \Nanimal in heat...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is somethin' else.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're alike.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So are his eyebrows thick?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, is he stupid, stubborn, and inflexible?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that either...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.24,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What, really? In that case, you should be glad they're not like each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many \Npeople like him.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If there were, everyone would be in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.67,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He even brags about his energy being his redeeming feature.{note}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.51,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a one-track mind and is totally oblivious.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruma, how are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. After all, I'm full of energy if nothing else.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aihara.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You change your hair? Looks pretty good on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The nerve of that guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When I cut mine shorter, he didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koume, \Nlet's give it our all.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.73,0:21:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, you're the only one giving it your all here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.99,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've got anything to do with Haruma or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.38,0:21:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've thought that my first boyfriend would be the bad-boy type.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard you already.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.49,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, they're so alike!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.49,0:21:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not going out with him because he acts like Haruma, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.56,0:21:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma knows that guy called Zenba, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.07,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.81,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Haruma say he admired him?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel \Nabout my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.87,0:21:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.51,0:22:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the year below.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be waiting outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of \Nperson is Zenba?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.40,0:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again, he's the leader, \Nso he's also the scariest.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.42,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone around him is easier to read, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.24,0:22:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Noro, he swings \Nfirst and asks later.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.62,0:22:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he sounds scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.59,0:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a little \Noverwhelmed sometimes too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.81,0:22:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it would take for me to be like those guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.74,0:22:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, \Nmy boyfriend...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.17,0:22:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up already, \Nnot him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.34,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of hearing \Nabout him, you idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.33,0:22:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wants to meet Zenba.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.06,0:22:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's stopping him?\NJust tell him to join the team.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.87,0:22:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't Zenba really scary?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.89,0:22:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the kindest \Nout of all of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.87,0:23:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.07,0:23:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say that\N he was the scariest?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.70,0:23:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the kindest\N and the scariest.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, is it difficult \Nto join the group?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.84,0:23:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is a lot like you, \NI swear.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.72,0:23:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I hope you didn't take that the wrong way.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.64,0:23:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense taken.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.76,0:23:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.04,0:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say I mean it, \NI really mean it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.64,0:23:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a no go, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.07,0:23:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have that \Nkind of pull yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.59,0:23:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the closest thing he's got to a brother, and even I'm not part of the family.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.10,0:23:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you only got in by luck and connections anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he is similar, \Nit'll be even more difficult. {idk why, implying haruma is ugly...?}{nah, implying new guy doesn't have the connections}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.90,0:24:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't take\N that the wrong way.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.38,0:24:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, big time.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.59,0:24:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my ultimate weapon! \NI'm always full of energy, you idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.48,0:24:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to be like Zenba Naito!\NLet's {fuckin'}go!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.05,0:24:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.09,0:24:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.32,0:24:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They local nutjobs or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.32,0:24:26.38,Top,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.38,0:24:27.38,Top,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.36,0:24:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see men doing that nowadays, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.36,0:24:28.84,Top,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.84,0:24:30.01,Top,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.01,0:24:31.01,Top,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:29.97,0:24:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.12,0:24:33.10,Top,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.10,0:24:34.18,Top,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:38.31,0:24:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You change your hair?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.37,0:24:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:42.69,0:24:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been rainy and humid lately, so it feels much better.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.11,0:24:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it suit me?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:48.03,0:24:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you ask him about that thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.27,0:24:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,About Linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:53.98,0:24:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I asked him! You might just be able to meet him.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.74,0:25:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you asked, they might even make you part of the team!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.23,0:25:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.60,0:25:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did I want to do that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.40,0:25:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought I wanted to join Linda?!\NYou've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.27,0:25:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd get me killed in a place like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.70,0:25:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Kacchan{note}, you're always talking about how amazing Zenba is.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.39,0:25:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I was being considerate by asking Haruma about him...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.73,0:25:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.30,0:25:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, you're a woman, so you probably don't get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:30.39,0:25:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could call it my dream, so even if I don't end up like him,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.78,0:25:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if the bad crowds gave \Nme some respect,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.45,0:25:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be nice to feel that, even if it all ended tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.02,0:25:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I live every \Nday covered in scars.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.36,0:25:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really think I get it, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:49.86,0:25:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That part of you that gets carried away and gets into trouble...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:53.49,0:25:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a lot like Haruma.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.28,0:26:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want him to lend me his Linda jacket for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.77,0:26:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:07.42,0:26:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That jacket gives you \Nsome serious status.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.96,0:26:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once I'd like to walk outside wearing that.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:12.51,0:26:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you ask Haruma or Zenba for that jacket to their face?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:20.73,0:26:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you take that \Nthe wrong way?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.96,0:26:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.98,0:26:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:25.52,0:26:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, you like me, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:29.36,0:26:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really did, you'd quit fussing and go get it for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:32.32,0:26:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so hung up on it?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.99,0:26:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I need it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.27,0:26:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:37.78,0:26:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had that, I could get money or anything else I want.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.16,0:26:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got a great idea in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.29,0:26:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if you did that, you'd be—
Dialogue: 10,0:26:46.54,0:26:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that got to do with you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:49.10,0:26:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If your boyfriend asks for it, then just shut up and bring it!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:58.89,0:27:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, I got this.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:01.35,0:27:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll make her do as I say.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.48,0:27:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aihara? What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:17.95,0:27:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:19.28,0:27:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:21.77,0:27:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is... I...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:24.64,0:27:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of breaking up with my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:27.06,0:27:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking up?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:28.59,0:27:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, or maybe just a break for a little while.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:32.46,0:27:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have been kinda rough lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.87,0:27:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. After I said how alike you two were.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:39.11,0:27:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:41.65,0:27:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:43.07,0:27:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did hope I'd run into you.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:47.35,0:27:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've finally got the courage to tell him.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:52.11,0:27:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was your own decision, \Nthen that's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:54.79,0:27:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take better care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:58.20,0:28:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, the thing is, Kacchan...{note}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:01.75,0:28:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want to talk to you or your leader, he just wanted that jacket.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.13,0:28:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is bright red! \NYou running a fever or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.16,0:28:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The leather is thick, \Nso it feels a little heavy.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:17.68,0:28:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, it's heavy in a whole other way.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:21.85,0:28:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll keep you warm.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.30,0:28:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't this really important to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:27.17,0:28:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it. You can take it in place of me walking you home.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:30.50,0:28:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be a race tonight, \Nbut you can return it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.30,0:28:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.65,0:28:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Chihiro! \NDon't go catching a cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:46.66,0:28:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsuhiko?\NIt's already fallen into our lap.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:56.95,0:28:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:58.22,0:29:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for you! It's not!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:03.43,0:29:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.55,0:29:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:08.53,0:29:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?\NKoume, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:13.38,0:29:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.65,0:29:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan{note} and his friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.88,0:29:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Took Haruma's jacket...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:24.90,0:29:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was only after the jacket from the start!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:31.13,0:29:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:38.34,0:29:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, guys... \NI'm not worthy of Linda's name!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:46.56,0:29:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:48.27,0:29:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, lend us some money.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:50.23,0:29:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the fuck do \Nyou think you are, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:53.43,0:29:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're part of Linda, that's who.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.24,0:30:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:02.18,0:30:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and give us your money.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:04.57,0:30:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm in Cobra!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.37,0:30:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that just perfect?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.16,0:30:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:11.02,0:30:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared shitless or what?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:16.80,0:29:29.83,Song,,0,0,0,,I was so excited I tore up the pages \Nof my diary and now I cry alone {エメラルドの恋 by 朝倉ゆかり; no lyrics either, but through some miracle found a clean version at least: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=znvMpO0bxfc}{はしゃぎすぎた日記帳のページ役に捨ててひとりで泣いた}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.48,0:29:43.37,Song,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be hated by him than\N endure kindness that isn't love.{彼に嫌われるより ずっと愛情じゃない 優しさが辛くて I think, fuck knows what it means}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:45.09,0:30:05.76,Song,,0,0,0,,The cold tears falling on my small chest \Nare trembling in the moonlight.{小さな胸に冷たく落ちる　涙の粒だ　月の光に震えてるわ}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.56,0:30:25.05,Song,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, take me somewhere \Nfar away and hold me tight.{ああ神様遠いどこかへあたしを連れ出して強く抱きしめて}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:26.09,0:30:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Linda did?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:29.21,0:30:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:37.65,0:30:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard... What do you think you're doing with that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:41.78,0:30:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're Aihara's boyfriend or whatever!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.57,0:30:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're gonna settle this! \NYou motherfucker!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:50.15,0:30:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.38,0:31:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:13.60,0:31:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Noro was attacked by Cobra?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:16.11,0:31:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We taught them a lesson and then asked what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:18.58,0:31:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But they said we're \Nthe ones who started it.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:22.49,0:31:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is that \Nsupposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:24.83,0:31:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Something doesn't sit right.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:27.87,0:31:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, what can we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:39.34,0:31:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn biker punks...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:43.17,0:31:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a nuisance!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:49.22,0:31:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You motherfucker...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:02.82,0:32:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,An idiot like you...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:07.64,0:32:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is just gonna get himself killed by the rest of Linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:11.38,0:32:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should've kept quiet about the jacket.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:15.02,0:32:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you listenin' to me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:20.16,0:32:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fuck with me, \Nyou bastard...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:25.43,0:32:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one tough son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:33.78,0:32:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:38.07,0:32:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You'll pay for this...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:48.91,0:32:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:54.22,0:32:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:56.98,0:32:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,fuckin' die already!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.83,0:33:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:22.12,0:33:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:33.93,0:33:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:35.31,0:33:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They all went white as a sheet and forked over their money, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.66,0:33:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make even more off 'em.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:42.10,0:33:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we should stick to guys that look shady.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:45.96,0:33:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If they haven't heard of Linda, it won't mean shit.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:04.43,0:34:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't freak out!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:05.98,0:34:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just the one guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:07.65,0:34:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how many of us there are! Get him! I said get him!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:12.65,0:34:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're in shit now...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:14.53,0:34:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:19.91,0:34:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:55.03,0:34:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please forgive me... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:57.97,0:35:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:25.10,0:35:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Motherfucker...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:27.01,0:35:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a dead man!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.38,0:35:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Z-Zenba?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.70,0:35:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:48.48,0:35:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I make excuses, \N hit me as much as you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:53.01,0:35:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just dead weight to everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:57.46,0:36:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be as cool as Maki...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:01.55,0:36:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Never be as tough as Noro...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:04.98,0:36:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think on \Nmy feet like Keizou...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:09.38,0:36:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm nothing like you!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:12.68,0:36:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lend it to someone that doesn't suit it.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:24.91,0:36:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go collapsing \Nbefore I hear the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:27.52,0:36:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to pull that same stunt on \Nmy seniors when I first joined Linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:32.05,0:36:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Noro once got into trouble when \Nhe beat up one of our founding members.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:36.92,0:36:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't let Maki know I told you.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.91,0:36:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But he couldn't even ride a bicycle until middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:44.37,0:36:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit tattered and there's some blood on it, but fix it up yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:50.45,0:36:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:56.15,0:36:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your scooter?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:59.11,0:37:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a hurry to get here, and I fell off and wrecked it.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:05.72,0:37:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your energy was your saving grace.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:08.79,0:37:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So quit cryin' on me.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:17.85,0:37:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? You're getting in the way of our race!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:23.18,0:37:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit fucking with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:24.56,0:37:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't settled things with Linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:27.18,0:37:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna settle it?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:29.31,0:37:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ain't that just perfect, dumbass?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.65,0:37:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, you bastard?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:36.66,0:37:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:40.41,0:37:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That mess the other \Nday was all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:44.93,0:37:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault! So, I'll be the one dealing with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:50.32,0:37:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you scared of?! Let's get this over with already!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:56.09,0:37:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's so funny?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:58.87,0:38:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, looks like you've got yourself another idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:02.96,0:38:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:03.94,0:38:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll settle this whole thing with a race!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:08.59,0:38:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit trying to act cool, you idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.76,0:38:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:26.08,0:38:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't crash this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:29.98,0:38:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Think there's a boy like Haruma out there?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:34.12,0:38:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:36.18,0:38:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest with me. Don't you actually have a thing for Haruma?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:43.10,0:38:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:48.12,0:38:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. But you should've seen the look on your face.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:51.34,0:38:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:14.02,0:39:28.36,Song,,0,0,0,,A blue crescent moon, an emergency stairwell,\Nworn-out clothes, the sound of silence.{it's a miracle, but we actually have lyrics for this one; https://utaten.com/lyric/to16065536/}{蒼い三日月 非常階段\Nくたびれた服静けさの音\Nつま先立ちに進む足どり\N明日がどこかわからないけど}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:28.36,0:39:36.21,Song,,0,0,0,,Tiptoeing forward,\NI don't know where tomorrow will be but...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:36.21,0:39:50.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Rhythms we can't ride, an old manual,\Nour time is inversely proportional. {乗れないリズム 古いマニュアル\N反比例する 僕たちの時間\Nちょっと変わったコミックスの様な\N危ない話にのってみたくなる}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:50.31,0:39:58.56,Song,,0,0,0,,I feel like getting into a dangerous story, \Nlike something from a twisted comic.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:58.56,0:40:15.61,Song,,0,0,0,,We're past the time of dreaming, \Nlike naked DNA without a map. {夢見る頃を過ぎた 僕たちまるで地図のない\N裸のD-N-A}{can you tell I haven't even tried?}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:20.29,0:40:34.26,Song,,0,0,0,,A dropped earring, a fickle wind, \Na streetlight gone out, a tall building. {落したピアス 気まぐれな風\N消えた街燈 背の高いビル\N伸ばした指にたったひとつの\N確かなものは君のぬくもりさ}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:34.27,0:40:42.82,Song,,0,0,0,,At the tip of my outstretched fingers,\N the one certain thing is the warmth of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:42.86,0:40:59.69,Song,,0,0,0,,We're past the time of dreaming, \Nlike naked DNA without a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.69,0:41:01.69,Song,,0,0,0,,
